# Git Workflow

## Branch Naming
- Feature: `feature/trainer-dashboard`
- Bugfix: `bugfix/login-crash`
- Hotfix: `hotfix/critical-security-issue`

## Commit Messages
```bash
# Conventional Commits 사용
feat: add trainer dashboard view
fix: resolve login token refresh issue
refactor: extract trainer card widget
docs: update README with setup instructions
test: add unit tests for auth repository
```

## Pre-commit Checklist
```bash
# 커밋 전 실행
dart format .
flutter analyze
flutter test

# CI/CD가 없다면 pre-commit hook 설정 권장
```
